{"tid":2107760,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始：呼籲私營機構安排員工在家工作","createTime":"2020-07-14T05:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T01:02:21.000Z","uid":212626,"like":55,"dislike":178,"uniUserReply":118,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0c41ab9b5bc1cdb119d4647611e9bbdbcefba5","tid":2107760,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T05:48:42.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局局長陳肇始在本台節目表示，如果市民現階段無任何病徵，但擔心感染新型冠狀病毒，可以到醫管局轄下18間中醫門診及地區康健中心取樣本瓶進行檢測，無需付費，當局正與醫管局及衛生署商討，爭取本周內擴至普通科門診亦可收集樣本瓶。她表示，隨檢測數量上升，確診個案數目有機會增加，對醫療系統構成壓力，醫管局必要時會調整服務。<br />\n<br />\n對於未有安排公務員在家工作，陳肇始表示，市民對政府有期望，部分公共服務要繼續，需作出平衡，但呼籲私營機構考慮安排員工在家工作。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346940\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2346940&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCnyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=9746a022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346940</a>"},{"pid":"bfbc6deb71fb5d23a2593b61af691cb83cb3366a","tid":2107760,"uid":213628,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"係先好講"},{"pid":"f411f350b2131dbdd1a3dfcae19f0733627c729b","tid":2107760,"uid":77187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48fc2627b7d1bd1090214625c48933ba365d8eb","tid":2107760,"uid":38533,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T05:50:02.000Z","msg":"有撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a705a443ce64540d91d6a7d1ff667fe1feca9da","tid":2107760,"uid":96704,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T05:50:35.000Z","msg":"呼籲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1eab0a0af4b59c1214dd27031df014c5f0f08f","tid":2107760,"uid":33635,"like":173,"dislike":0,"score":173,"citedBy":5,"replyTim